Name: Endless Darkness
Desc:
[Dark Magic]
Endless darkness rises from within enemies to consume them. Activated when you use Dark or Equilibrium skills during Eclipse or Equilibrium. Shares cooldown with Eternal Lightness.
Also, permanently enhances Ender VI.
